$ON_TASLNKLAG
Onevent AFTER_CHANGE Gosub AMM_TASLNKLAG From W1PJMTAS3
Return

$AMM_TASLNKLAG
Call AM_TASLNKLAG(zc)
If !mkstat & GOBJET
 zoncou = "TASLNKLAG" : Gosub APRES_MODIF From =GPROGRAMME
